to execute, run "./run.sh"

this project is a basic copy of the arcade game asteroids
controlled with ARROW_UP to move forward, ARROW_LEFT and ARROW_RIGHT to turn
and ARROW_DOWN for a short teleport forward

difficulty increases over time, and score is accumulated by destroying asteroids, with the
exact amount determined by the size of the asteroid destroyed

press ESCAPE to pause the game

after a game over, press Q to quit, or A to play again
